# Project PoG

A python implementation of the famous WWI wargame, Paths of Glory(1999).

To learn about the game itself, see BoardGameGeek for detail: https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/91/paths-glory.
You can also learn about the game from an anti-war movie with the same name, Paths of Glory(1957) by Stanley Kubrick.

### Current Progress
- Frontend: TBD
- Backend: TBD
- Model: Python
  - common.py: config file
  - units.py: define all the units in the game
  - scenarios.py: define the unit status in scenarios
  - battle.py: battle, take loss, etc.
